    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Click on the SplitContainer panels with a mouse button and a message will be shown. <br />The message shows which panel was clicked.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>SplitContainer </em>and panels&nbsp;have the&nbsp;<em>Click </em>and other events.<br />The <em>Click </em>event occurs when user clicking with a mouse button.</p>]]></Paragraph>
